229
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:27,046
Dapat!

230
00:17:29,799 --> 00:17:31,134
Awas!

231
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:42,520
Otonoshin!

232
00:17:52,822 --> 00:17:54,866
Kita tiba di Goryokaku!

